### Rockerbox vs Northbeam

| Factor | Northbeam | Rockerbox |
|--------|-----------|-----------|
| Digital attribution | ✓ Strong | ✓ Good |
| Podcast tracking | Limited | ✓ Strong |
| TV/OTT | Limited | ✓ Strong |
| MMM included | ✗ No | ✓ Yes |
| Starting price | $400/mo | $200/mo |
| Use case | Tactical media buying | Strategic CMO decisions |

### Why Rockerbox Over Northbeam

Northbeam excels at digital performance marketing. Rockerbox captures brand/awareness channels that drive demand but don't get direct clicks.

### Best For

