## 5. SegmentStream — Best for Cookieless Future

**Why consider SegmentStream:** AI-driven attribution designed for a world without cookies.

### SegmentStream vs Northbeam

| Factor | Northbeam | SegmentStream |
|--------|-----------|---------------|
| Cookie dependency | First-party focused | Cookieless-first |
| AI approach | ML fractional credit | Visit scoring + prediction |
| Incrementality | ✗ No | ✓ Geo holdout validation |
| Privacy focus | Standard | Strong |
| Pricing | Pageview-based | Custom |

### Why SegmentStream Over Northbeam

SegmentStream's "Visit Scoring" measures impact without relying on traditional conversion tracking. As privacy restrictions tighten, this forward-looking approach may prove more durable.

### Best For

- Brands preparing for cookie deprecation
- Those concerned about iOS/privacy impacts
- Forward-thinking measurement teams
- High-consideration purchases where visit quality matters

